Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H20218E&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Cruiser! X Rider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke's father, Professor Jin was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,His father was killed by the great evil organization GOD's pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mizuki Ryouko, Keisuke's lover, was the one who guided GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed by his lover and his father killed,\NKeisuke also died once from GOD's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And with his father's skills Keisuke revived as a modified human, a Kaizorg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X was like the sea, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...Keisuke's heart was distressed, \Nas his body was now no longer human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke just kept riding his motorcycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, it seemed the only way he could calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...was to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I really need to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Ryouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You even know my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a normal human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have time to be depressed about the death of your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...or to follow your lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can decide what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're everyone's X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you must have witnessed those many people with tools in their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But, yet you were obsessed with that woman, Ryouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you forgot about those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If they committed a mass murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, you are to protect the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A pickaxe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you were probably hypnotized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnotized?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnotized?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anything strange happen to you before you lost consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When our exchange meeting with the apartment next door was done...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We went out to the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember, until that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember. It was a flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I do recall the sound of a flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! How dare a child hypnotize adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That child is merely playing the flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a lone boy who lost her father in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To say that he hypnotized you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's quite a distance from the apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this sound be heard from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD Warfare Agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it, it was you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your father, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...died as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my father's flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have loved your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We were always quarreling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I really loved him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, I kept disobeying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Susumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I look shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm crying because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look shameful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But... there's something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD General Commander. \NGive Pannic the following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider has started moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And kill every human in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You make sure the devilish homicide plan succeeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of a flute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same melody as before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Up there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jin Keisuke, with his Redizer and Perfecter, Sets Up into Kamen Rider X!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They did this to us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going to kill people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of that flute. It's Susumu's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to cover for that kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to kill my customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to do something about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be forced to kill people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch that brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pannic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD General Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My plan is proceeding well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With using the flute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...they'll be able to commit murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Use those foolish humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...and kill X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be that Yaokichi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! You're part of them as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Susumu is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else was playing the flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You should die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he do with that knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not human anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Susumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Only robots can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Robots don't have fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That story you told me was a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Susumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you! You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me that you just lost your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to me, Susumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a robot! Don't pretend to be a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really not a human anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've arrived, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, I... was hated by a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me that I was a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes on like this, I don't think I can protect children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because children run away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But, father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a human, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm Jin Keisuke, I'm a human, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. You aren't a human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't affected by Pannic's flute...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...because you're a modified human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Have pride in not being a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Who else is out there that can fight against GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider. Be a person who can have pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...in being able to resist something no human can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a great modified human!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that I miscalculated something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be of use to you, to be able to fight against the great GOD organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The existence of this Jin Station has the ability of making you a weaker human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to come crying to the Jin Station every time something happens, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. You know this, you must fight alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Without relying on anyone, with your own powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke. This Jin Station shouldn't have existed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll surely become the X Rider you told me to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand me over that flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my father's flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing strange with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...that it's not the flute's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the kid himself with his strange powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! He must be some kind of devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Three wives in the apartment have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}must{\i0} be his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey everyone! What should we do with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill Susumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at who was playing the flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You made us believe it was that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a cyborg of GOD, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems this time has come, Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an elite of GOD, Pannic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move, I'll take his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sometimes good to not be a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep this safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why you weren't affected by Pannic...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...was because your ears were accustomed to the sounds of your flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke was able to grasp confidence and pride in this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one person able to fight against GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The one person capable of destroying GOD, again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...is him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:22:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Ryouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is Kiriko's true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the day the GOD organization is annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Assassination Dark Spider Operation!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider